Supara Group is a leading menswear and womenswear apparel company in Southeast Asia with over 400 point-of-sales across Thailand, the Philippines, Malaysia, and Indonesia. Established in the 1970s, the Group brand portfolio includes GQ, Giffini, and CL,. The Group is vertically integrated with its own factories established across Thailand. This is to ensure our product is of the highest quality ranging from great design, comfortable fit, and detailed craftsmanship. Our growth strategy is to forge our expertise in developing technical and functional garments and creating a true omni-channel retail shopping experience for our customers

